<p>There are numerous ways to approach this, but that one seemed like the optimal one to me.</p>

<p>The migration process converted all Disqus comments to guest comments in Hyvor, which is a bit unfortunate, but unavoidable.
Still, I think thatâ€™s a small price to pay for a privacy-focused solution with better usability. I hope that this transition
will result in more interesting discussions taking place here!</p>
